<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      background-color: #e9e3e3;
      padding: 2rem 5rem;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #eef2ff;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px 0px rgba(55, 48, 163, 0.08);
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header h3 {
      margin: 0;
      margin-left: 0.2rem;
    }

    .header button {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--Indigo-indigo-600, #4f46e5);
      background: var(--Base-White, #fff);
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 0;
      margin-left: 1rem;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 2rem 5rem 1.8rem 5rem;
    }

    .content h4 {
      margin: 0 0 0.2rem 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
      line-height: 1.5rem;
    }

    .verifyEmail table {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.8rem 4rem;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .verifyEmail {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer {
      background: var(--Neutral-Grey-50, #f8fafc);
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .footer p {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .footer .Unsubscribe-wrapper span {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #475569;
      color: var(--Neutral-Grey-600, #475569);
    }

    .footer .Unsubscribe-wrapper .border-height {
      height: 0.5rem;
      border-left: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .footer .social-mediaIcon-align tr td {
      padding: 0 0.8rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <button>JOB PORTAL</button>
      <table align="center">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <table>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://imgur.com/YOg2KXR.png" alt="profile-icon" />
                </td>
                <td>
                  <h3>Verify your email address</h3>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h4>Hi {{name}} ðŸ‘‹,</h4>
      <h4>Welcome to RGT Job Portal</h4>
      <p>
        Please click the button below to verify your email address. If you did
        not sign up to RGT, please ignore this email or contact us at
        contact@ratnaglobaltech.com
      </p>
      <h4>Tom Tompson</h4>
      <h4>RGT Support Team</h4>
      <a href={{link}} class="verifyEmail">
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td style="color: white;">
              Verify email
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <table align="center">
        <tr class="Unsubscribe-wrapper">
          <td><span>Unsubscribe</span></td>
          <td class="border-height">
            <div></div>
          </td>
          <td><span>Report a problem</span></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>
        You have received this mail because your e-mail ID is registered with jobportal.com. This is a system-generated
        e-mail,
        please don't reply to this message.
        <br>
        Please do not pay any money to anyone who promises to find you a job. jobportal shall not have any
        responsibility in this
        regard. We recommend that you visit our Terms & Conditions and the Security Advice for more information.
      </p>
      <table align="center" class="social-mediaIcon-align">
        <tr>
          <td align="center">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ratnaglobaltech" class="achorforLogo">
              <img src="https://imgur.com/5Dz2dXb.png" alt="facebook" class="socialLogo">
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ratnaglobaltech" class="achorforLogo">
              <img src="https://imgur.com/KdWIvnJ.png" alt="instagram" class="socialLogo">
            </a>

            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/ratnaglobaltech" class="achorforLogo">
              <img src="https://imgur.com/pP6FASo.png" alt="linkedin" class="socialLogo">
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>